Source: libnfs
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Andres Mejia <amejia@debian.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.0.50~)
Standards-Version: 3.9.2
Homepage: https://github.com/sahlberg/libnfs
